Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 艾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你好精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明明還沒吃早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你幾歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,5歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我11歲 和你們兩個一樣大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是最年長的
